n\n## Tasks\n- [ ] Add `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` block with `:root` variable overrides\n- [ ] Override hardcoded `#fff` backgrounds in inputs, chat-messages, output-box, screenshot-image\n- [ ] Override hardcoded status/message modifier class colors for dark readability\n- [ ] Update `color-scheme` in `:root` to `light dark`\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
